    <h1>Should You Eat Protein<br><span class="accent">Before Bed?</span></h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">For decades, experts told us not to eat after 7pm. That advice made sense once — but it wasn't built for men over 40 trying to hold onto muscle. Here's what actually happens while you sleep.</p>
    <p class="hero-meta">By Robert · May 2, 2026 · 7 min read</p>
